Beep Me is not prompting you for a review, since we don't want to disturb your workflow.
If you feel generous we will very appreciate your review on AppStore.

As always, if you need any support, please contact us with the support mail - leaving a feedback on the app store is not something that we can reply on..

Thank you and enjoy the new version!

Updates to the app look & feel.
Supporting a new Auto theme in iOS 13+ to dynamically change to Dark mode when needed.
New custom repeat options!
iPad users can now use Beep Me side-by-side other apps.

Thanks for all the great feedback!
